ser</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/1/02 5:32:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23103.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Writing notes...</span><hr size=1> Now this is truely a unique idea <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>The stuff for notes could be tradeskills:<br><br>(Feather)Pens are made by fletchers<br><br>Paper and binders are made by Tailors<br><br>Ink (and .. of course invisible ink) are made by rogues with the make poison skill.<br><br>About space for these notes on EQ-servers. Skip the messageboards. Hardly no one uses them. EQ must have allocated some space for them. Then the space could be reclaimed for the notes.<br><br><br><br><br> <p><br>Solonote Crescendo<br>20 bard<br>Member of the Freeport Reserve Militia<br>The Tribunal</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufinneus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Finneus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/1/02 8:50:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23103.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Writing notes...</span><hr size=1> There actually is..or was (haven't looked in way over a year)..a way for players to post notes in game.  In select locations in game there are bulliten boards on the wall that you can post up notes on.  I seem to recall one in qeunos and maybe one in freeport or highkeep.  They tend to be in out of the way taverns. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91155>Finneus Fingers</a>, Karana<BR>60 Rogue<BR><BR>"click...creaaak"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukenwoodx2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kenwoodx2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/1/02 9:42:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23103.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.swbell.net/kenwoodx/images/greenguy.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Writing notes...</span><hr size=1> Yes the bulletin boards do exist in game and they actually work.. problem is I don't think anyone actually uses them enough for them to be of much use..   <p><table><tr><td><table><tr align=center><td style="filter:glow(color=green strength=5);font-family:arial;font-weight:bold;font-size:'12pt'"><font color=#FFFF99>Vargus Wolvendrac</font></td></tr><tr align=center><td style="filter:glow(color=green strength=3);font-family:arial;font-weight:bold;font-size:'10pt'"><font color=#FFFF99>Barbarian Warrior</font></td></tr><tr align=center><td style="font-family:garamond;font-weight:bold;font-size:'10pt'"><font color=green><I>Crystalline Dragons of Xegony</I></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><table></td></tr></table><TABLE BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF="http://blog.ravenblack.net/quiz/videogame.pl"><IMG BORDER=0 ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=80 SRC="http://blog.ravenblack.net/quiz/videogame/14.png" ALT="What Video Game Character Are You? I am a Gauntlet Adventurer." /></A>I am <B>a Gauntlet Adventurer</B>.<BR /><BR />I strive to improve my living conditions by hoarding gold, food, and sometimes keys and potions. I love adventure, fighting, and particularly winning - especially when there's a p